@node what_is_this "What is Mr Convert?"

             (¯`·._.·' Mr Convert `·._.·'¯)


         (_.·'¯`· What is Mr Convert? ·'¯`·._)


 I make graphics and homepages on PC, just cuz'
 I don't have money to expand my Amiga...

 I have them connected since I often need to
 copy files from one to the other.

 I found out that I was in a need of an easy
 to use text-converter.
    I looked for one but I couldn't find any
 that suited my specific needings.

 So I made one!

  But, hey, I guess more people that are in
  need of it.. so here you are!

  Hope you'll like it!
@endnode
